high_descs: Move a bit to the left of the shelf.
Pick up a game controller from the shelf.
Turn around and walk straight to the sidetable.
Place the controller on the sidetable.

high_descs: Turn around and face the shelf.

Put the controller on the sidetable.

Pick the controller from the shelf.
Turn left and walk towards the side table.
Place the controller on the side table.
anns.task_desc: To place the controller on the side table.
